profile: Here at Windsor Handyman we can handle any size of job, from a one hour repair to a complete bathroom or kitchen remodel. We are skilled at installing doors, windows, drywall, plumbing, painting, flooring, carpentry, and so much more. We handle the jobs the big contractors don't want.
